<h1>HUUNNNGEEER... FOR BOOOORRRRGAAAAARRRR! HEEEERETIC, BORGAAARRRRRR!</h1>

<h2>Uneaten Deliciousness</h2>

<ul>
    {{#each burgers}}
        {{#unless eaten}}
            {{> burger-interface eat=true}}
        {{/unless}}
    {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>"Mmm! This IS a tasty burger!" - Jules Winnfield </h2>

<ul>
    {{#each burgers}}
        {{#if eaten}}
            {{> burger-interface eat=false}}
        {{/if}}
    {{/each}}
</ul>

<h2>"Order up, Squidwaaard!"</h2>
<form class="create-form">

    <div class="form-group">
        <label for="ca">Whaddya want?</label>
        <input type="text" id="ca" name="flavor">
    </div>

    <button type="submit">Place Order</button>
</form>